<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 12:27:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>增强肠脑通讯可逆转衰老小鼠的认知衰退并改善记忆形成</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/enhancing-gut-brain-communication-reversed-cognitive-decline-improved-memory-formation-in-aging-mice</link><description>看到一盘美味的烤宽面条或节日火腿的香气肯定会让饥饿的肚子咕咕叫，期待着一场盛宴的到来。但是，尽管我们都体验过食物进入嘴巴之前用眼睛和鼻子“吃”的感觉，但对信息高速公路（称为迷走神经）的了解却少之又少，它向相反的方向发送信号——从肠道直接发送到大脑。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/enhancing-gut-brain-communication-reversed-cognitive-decline-improved-memory-formation-in-aging-mice.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 12:27:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/enhancing-gut-brain-communication-reversed-cognitive-decline-improved-memory-formation-in-aging-mice</guid></item><item><title>中性粒细胞胞外陷阱的循环标志物对急性胸痛患者长期预后的影响</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/circulating-markers-of-neutrophil-extracellular-traps-for-long%e2%80%90term-prognosis-in-patients-with-acute-chest-pain</link><description>使用人工智能绘制全脑细胞图谱&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/circulating-markers-of-neutrophil-extracellular-traps-for-longe28090term-prognosis-in-patients-with-acute-chest-pain2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 12:12:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/circulating-markers-of-neutrophil-extracellular-traps-for-long%e2%80%90term-prognosis-in-patients-with-acute-chest-pain</guid></item><item><title>长期研究证实，花粉替代饲料可增强蜜蜂群落</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/pollen-replacing-feed-strengthens-honey-bee-colonies-long-term-study-confirms</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 11:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/pollen-replacing-feed-strengthens-honey-bee-colonies-long-term-study-confirms</guid></item><item><title>常压超导体打破温度记录</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/room-pressure-superconductor-breaks-temperature-record</link><description>使用快速压力淬火技术，研究人员在环境压力下以创纪录的 151 K 保存了超导体中的亚稳态相。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/room-pressure-superconductor-breaks-temperature-record2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 11:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/room-pressure-superconductor-breaks-temperature-record</guid></item><item><title>NASA 的 DART 撞击实际上改变了小行星系统绕太阳的轨道</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/nasas-dart-impact-actually-changed-an-asteroid-systems-orbit-around-the-sun</link><description>NASA 的 DART 任务证明，航天器可以推动太空中的小行星系统，为行星防御提供了真正的考验。美国宇航局的 DART（双小行星重定向测试）航天器改变了太空中小行星系统的运动，证明动能撞击器可能是一种可行的方法&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nasas-dart-impact-actually-changed-an-asteroid-systems-orbit-around-the-sun.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 11:27:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/nasas-dart-impact-actually-changed-an-asteroid-systems-orbit-around-the-sun</guid></item><item><title>月球岩石挑战了长期以来关于地球水起源的理论</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/moon-rocks-challenge-long-held-theory-about-the-origin-of-earths-water</link><description>对月球土壤的氧同位素分析显示，大约 40 亿年前，陨石只向地月系统输送了有限数量的水。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/moon-rocks-challenge-long-held-theory-about-the-origin-of-earths-water.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 11:12:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/moon-rocks-challenge-long-held-theory-about-the-origin-of-earths-water</guid></item><item><title>新的 DNA 工具在检测野生动物遗传风险方面优于传统方法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-dna-tools-outperform-traditional-methods-for-detecting-genetic-risk-in-wildlife</link><description>通常由于栖息地丧失，野生动物种群变得小而孤立，不可避免地会经历近亲繁殖，这可能导致适应性丧失并最终灭绝。一种解决方案是进行基因拯救：一种管理干预措施，通过将外来者引入种群来引入新鲜血液，以减少近亲繁殖并恢复多样性。但研究人员如何知道近亲繁殖问题已经解决了呢？ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-dna-tools-outperform-traditional-methods-for-detecting-genetic-risk-in-wildlife.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 10:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-dna-tools-outperform-traditional-methods-for-detecting-genetic-risk-in-wildlife</guid></item><item><title>100个太阳质量的黑洞合并会激起时空涟漪，并可能在伽马射线中闪烁</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-100-solar-mass-black-hole-merger-ripples-spacetime-and-may-flash-in-gamma-rays</link><description>来自中国和意大利的一个国际团队报告了 2017 年具有里程碑意义的多信使发现可能的宇宙重演。 2024 年 11 月，LIGO-Virgo-KAGRA 天文台检测到来自双黑洞合并的引力波，编号为 S241125n。值得注意的是，仅仅几秒钟后，卫星就记录到了同一天空区域的短暂伽马射线爆发（GRB）。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-100-solar-mass-black-hole-merger-ripples-spacetime-and-may-flash-in-gamma-rays.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 10:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-100-solar-mass-black-hole-merger-ripples-spacetime-and-may-flash-in-gamma-rays</guid></item><item><title>量子点按需生成纠缠光子对</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/quantum-dots-generate-entangled-photon-pairs-on-demand</link><description>中国的研究人员首次展示了如何设计量子点来持续产生纠缠光子对。通过仔细定制单个量子点周围的光子环境，该团队表明可以以惊人的效率产生高度相关的光子对，这可能为新兴量子技术带来新的机遇。这项工作由北京量子信息科学研究院袁志良领导，发表在&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-dots-generate-entangled-photon-pairs-on-demand2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 10:27:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/quantum-dots-generate-entangled-photon-pairs-on-demand</guid></item><item><title>量子计算机在解决量子化学问题之前必须克服主要技术障碍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/quantum-computers-must-overcome-major-technical-hurdles-before-tackling-quantum-chemistry-problems</link><description>尽管量子计算的潜在应用很广泛，但一项新的可行性研究表明，量子计算机在解决量子化学问题方面仍然面临重大障碍。研究， &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-computers-must-overcome-major-technical-hurdles-before-tackling-quantum-chemistry-problems2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 10:12:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/quantum-computers-must-overcome-major-technical-hurdles-before-tackling-quantum-chemistry-problems</guid></item></channel></rss>